name: src/module/plugin/syntax/AbstractSyntaxLoader.js
AbstractSyntaxLoader
description:
Provides the base implementation for all syntax loader plugins which automatically associates member methods
to syntax definitions invoking the method with escomplex settings and assigning the result to the same name as
the method.

name: onLoadSyntax
description: Loads all member methods including from child classes that are not `constructor` or `onConfigure`.

name: s_GET_ALL_PROPERTY_NAMES
description: Walks an objects inheritance tree collecting property names stopping before `AbstractSyntaxLoader` is reached.

name: src/module/report/AbstractReport.js
AbstractReport
description:
Provides several helper methods to work with method oriented data stored as `this.aggregate` in `ClassReport` /
`ModuleReport` and directly in `MethodReport`.

name: constructor
description:
If given assigns the method report to an internal variable. This is used by `ClassReport` and `ModuleReport`
which stores a `MethodReport` respectively in `this.aggregate`.

params.name: methodReport
params.description: A MethodReport to associate with this report.
params.descriptionRaw: A MethodReport to associate with this report.

name: _methodReport
description: Stores any associated MethodReport.

name: finalize
description: Cleans up any house keeping member variables.

name: methodReport
description:
Returns the associated `MethodReport` or `this`. Both ClassReport and ModuleReport have an `aggregate`
MethodReport.

name: incrementDistinctHalsteadItems
description: Increments the associated MethodReport HalsteadData for distinct identifiers.

name: incrementHalsteadItems
description: Increments the associated MethodReport Halstead items including distinct and total counts.

name: incrementHalsteadMetric
description: Increments the associated MethodReport Halstead metric type.

name: incrementParams
description: Increments the associated MethodReport parameter count.

name: isHalsteadMetricDistinct
description: Returns true if a given HalsteadData metric / identifier is not found in the associated MethodReport.

name: _scopeStackMethod

name: srcPath
description:
Stores the active source path of the module / file. This path is respective of how the file is referenced in
the source code itself. `srcPath` is only defined as supplied when processing projects.

name: srcPathAlias
description:
Stores the active source path alias of the module / file. This path is respective of how the file is
referenced in the source code itself when aliased including NPM and JSPM modules which provide a `main` entry.
`srcPathAlias` is only defined as supplied when processing projects.

name: src/project/result/ProjectResult.js
ProjectResult
description: Provides the default project report object which stores data pertaining to all modules / files contained.

name: constructor
description: Initializes ProjectReport with default values.

params.name: moduleReports
params.description: An array of ModuleReports for each module / file processed.
params.descriptionRaw: An array of ModuleReports for each module / file processed.

params.name: settings
params.description: An object hash of the settings used in generating this report via ESComplexProject.
params.descriptionRaw:
An object hash of the settings used in generating this report via
                                         ESComplexProject.

name: settings
description: Stores the settings used to generate the project report.

name: adjacencyList
description:
Stores a compacted form of the adjacency matrix. Each row index corresponds to the same report index.
Each row entry corresponds to a report index. These relationships dictate the dependencies between all
report ModuleReports given the source paths.

name: changeCost
description:
Measures the average percentage of modules affected when one module / file in the project is changed.
Lower is better.

name: coreSize
description:
Measures the percentage of modules that are widely depended on which also depend on other modules.
Lower is better.

name: cyclomatic
description: Measures the average method cyclomatic complexity for the project.

name: effort
description: Measures the average method maintenance effort for the project.

name: firstOrderDensity
description:
Measures the percentage of all possible internal dependencies that are actually realized in the project.
Lower is better.

name: loc
description: Measures the average method logical SLOC (source lines of code) for the project.

name: maintainability
description: Measures the average method maintainability index for the project.

name: params
description: Measures the average number of method parameters for the project.

name: reports
description: Stores all ModuleReport data for the project sorted by the module / files `srcPath`.

name: visibilityList
description:
Stores a compacted form of the visibility matrix. Each row index corresponds to the same report index.
Each row entry corresponds to a report index. These relationships dictate the reverse visibility between all
report ModuleReports which may indirectly impact the given module / file.

name: finalize
description:
Finalizes the ProjectResult. If `settings.serializeReports` is false output just `filePath`, `srcPath` &
`srcPathAlias` entries of reports.

name: parse
description: Deserializes a JSON object representing a ProjectResult.

params.name: object
params.description: A JSON object of a ProjectResult that was previously serialized.
params.descriptionRaw: A JSON object of a ProjectResult that was previously serialized.

name: toStringAdjacency
description:
Returns a string representing the adjacency relationships by printing out the report index followed by
dependent ModuleReport indices / `srcPaths`.

name: toStringVisibility
description:
Returns a string representing the visibilty relationships by printing out the report index followed by
indirect reverse dependency ModuleReport indices / `srcPaths`.

name: src/utils/MathUtil.js
MathUtil
description: Provides common math utilities.

name: compactMatrix
description:
Compacts a 2D matrix testing entries against a testValue with a default value of `1` for inclusion. The resulting
compacted list has an array per row with entries that correspond to the column index that passed the test.

params.name: testValue
params.description: A value to test strict equality to include entry for compaction.
params.descriptionRaw: A value to test strict equality to include entry for compaction.

name: create2DArray
description: Creates an 2-dimensional array of the given length.

params.name: length
params.descriptionRaw: Array length for x / y dimensions.

name: getMedian
description:
Returns the median / middle value from the given array after sorting numerically. If values length is odd the
middle value in the array is returned otherwise if even two middle values are summed then divided by 2.

name: getPercent
description: Returns the percent of a given value and limit.

params.name: value
params.description: A value to calculate the percentage against the given limit.
params.descriptionRaw: A `value` to calculate the percentage against the given `limit`.
